{
  "stem": "4361.8",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And as he said, as he was rolling down with the Russian army, he scoured every camp on his way to look for his parents, and he never found them.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that evening, he invited me to a dance, and I went and a romance started.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I was very fearful [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that I don't want to lose again.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I have had so many losses but there was something else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He helped me cry for the first time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he was telling me how he went from camp to camp looking for his parents and how he knew what I went through.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he looked at my number, and that's when I cried.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he said, you know, [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Bubika, ?] if I could lessen your pain by taking that number onto me, I would.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That was the first time in all that time that somebody [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] shared with me and-- and-- and wanted to make me feel better and understood and understood.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But there was a problem, because Sighet being a fairly small town, it was not very well-regarded that a Russian-- I mean, you know, he didn't have a sign saying, I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But, I mean, he wore the red uniform.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So first of all, it was a terrible thing that this Fischman [? boy ?] is involved with a Russian officer.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "That was not too good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And from his point of view, particularly since where my sister-in-law lived and I lived with them, the Russian Kommandatura was just across the street.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And Leonid would come regularly to visit, and-- and-- you know, he would take me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I saw Popov, the-- the big Russian clown, because he came to entertain the army.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
